ZH: 我感冒了，鼻孔都堵住了。
EN: I have caught a cold, both of my nostrils are blocked.

ZH: 当他大笑时，他的鼻孔会变得很大。
EN: When he laughs, his nostrils get really wide.

ZH: 她从左鼻孔呼出一股烟。
EN: She exhaled smoke from her left nostril.

ZH: 他在咳嗽时，可以看到他的鼻孔在疼痛。
EN: You can see his nostrils hurting when he coughs.

ZH: 她通过鼻孔嗅到了美味的蛋糕香味。
EN: She smelled the delicious cake aroma through her nostrils.

ZH: 他的鼻孔里有一只小虫子。
EN: There's a little bug in his nostrils.

ZH: 我的右鼻孔总是比左鼻孔更敏感。
EN: My right nostril is always more sensitive than the left one.

ZH: 医生用药棉塞在病人的鼻孔中。
EN: The doctor placed a cotton pad in the patient's nostrils.

ZH: 外面空气冷得让我的鼻孔感到刺痛。
EN: The air outside is so cold it stings my nostrils.

ZH: 她用力吸了一口气，鼻孔膨胀了起来。
EN: She took a deep breath, and her nostrils expanded.

ZH: 他在鼻孔前嗅了一下鲜花的香味。
EN: He sniffed the scent of the flowers in front of his nostrils.

ZH: 孩子流鼻血，鼻孔里受伤了。
EN: The child's nosebleed indicates injury inside the nostril.

ZH: 我深吸了一口气，鼻孔充满了新鲜空气。
EN: I took a deep breath, and my nostrils filled with fresh air.

ZH: 他擤了一下鼻孔，把鼻涕吹到纸巾上。
EN: He blew his nostrils and wiped the mucus on a tissue.

ZH: 这个药可以缓解鼻孔过敏的症状。
EN: This medicine can alleviate the symptoms of allergic nostrils.

ZH: 当他紧张时，他的鼻孔会不自然地扩张。
EN: When he gets nervous, his nostrils expand unnaturally.

ZH: 它闻了闻空气，试图找到食物的香味，但只从鼻孔里喷出了气体。
EN: It sniffed the air, trying to locate the scent of food, but only exhaled gases from its nostrils.

ZH: 我能闻到一股奇怪的味道，它从那个古老建筑的鼻孔中散发出来。
EN: I can smell a bizarre odor emanating from the nostrils of that old building.

ZH: 她往鼻孔里滴了几滴盐水，以清洁鼻腔。
EN: She dropped a few drops of saline solution into her nostrils to clean her nasal passage.

ZH: 当他流泪时，咸水溢出了他的鼻孔。
EN: Salty tears overflowed from his nostrils when he cried.

ZH: 我在鼻孔里塞了块止血纱布，以止住鼻血。
EN: I inserted a piece of gauze into my nostril to stop the nosebleed.
